        'reciprocating-saws' => '<p class="lead">Reciprocating saws excel at demolition, remodeling, and pruning. Here are the best options we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DCS382B</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DCS382B</strong> 20V MAX XR brushless reciprocating saw delivers 2,900 SPM with a 1-1/8" stroke length. The tool-free blade change makes swapping blades quick and easy.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07YD3L45V?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Corded: Milwaukee 6538-21</h2><p>For all-day demolition work, this 15-amp Super Sawzall delivers unstoppable power. The constant power technology maintains speed under heavy load.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000065CJL?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: BLACK+DECKER BDCR20C</h2><p>This 20V MAX cordless recip saw handles occasional demolition and pruning at an accessible price. Variable speed trigger gives you control on delicate cuts.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00OB3RR5C?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Milwaukee 2821-21</h2><p>The M18 FUEL Super Sawzall cuts 30% faster than competitors with a one-key compatible design. Adjustable orbital action and anti-vibration technology reduce fatigue.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08FXJCF6Q?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Compact: Makita XRJ05Z</h2><p>At just 14.5 inches long, this compact reciprocating saw fits into tight spaces. Brushless motor and 1-1/4" stroke still deliver serious cutting performance.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N78DJQ6?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'oscillating-multi-tools' => '<p class="lead">Oscillating multi-tools handle dozens of tasks with one tool. Here are the best we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DCS356B</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DCS356B</strong> 20V MAX XR oscillating tool offers a 1.8-degree oscillation arc and 3-speed selector. The quick-change accessory system swaps blades in seconds without tools.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07YD55Y43?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Milwaukee 2836-20</h2><p>Milwaukee\'s M18 FUEL multi-tool leads with tool-free blade change and the REDLINK Plus intelligence system. Variable speed dial goes from 11,000 to 18,000 OPM.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B083GMDBR3?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Corded: Fein FMM350QSL</h2><p>Fein invented the oscillating tool, and their corded MultiMaster remains the gold standard. German engineering delivers precision and durability that lasts decades.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07VBGT9KH?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: RYOBI P343B</h2><p>RYOBI\'s ONE+ oscillating tool gets you into the platform affordably. LED work light and universal blade adapter handle most home improvement tasks.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08F6S1QZ8?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Kit: Makita XMT03Z</h2><p>Makita\'s 18V LXT multi-tool with soft start and variable speed works flawlessly for trim work, electrical cuts, and detail sanding. Accepts OIS and Starlock blades.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00UD7N0AI?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'angle-grinders' => '<p class="lead">Angle grinders are essential for metalworking, masonry, and more. Here are the best we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DCG413B</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DCG413B</strong> 20V MAX XR 4.5" angle grinder features a kickback brake and e-clutch system for maximum safety. Brushless motor delivers 9,000 RPM.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07BS8G2TN?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Corded: Makita GA4553R</h2><p>This 11-amp 4.5" grinder includes an SJS Super Joint System to protect the gear housing. Auto-stop brush system shuts down the motor when brushes need replacing.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07H8J2P8D?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: BLACK+DECKER BDEG400</h2><p>A capable 6-amp grinder for occasional metalwork and DIY projects. The 3-position side handle improves control and comfort.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0073ZZRCY?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Milwaukee 2880-21</h2><p>Milwaukee\'s M18 FUEL 4.5/5" grinder delivers the power of 13-amp corded tools wirelessly. RAPIDSTOP brake stops the wheel in under 2 seconds.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08T9JCMTZ?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Large: DeWalt DWE4517</h2><p>For heavy-duty grinding, this 7" corded grinder delivers 8,500 RPM with 4.7 HP. Dust ejection system extends motor life in harsh environments.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00FMFLB9S?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'random-orbital-sanders' => '<p class="lead">A quality random orbital sander makes quick work of finishing and prep. Here are the best we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DWE6423K</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DWE6423K</strong> 5" random orbital sander features a variable speed dial (8,000-12,000 OPM) and dust-sealed switch. The dust collection bag captures over 97% of particles.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B007NVSSFS?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Festool ETS EC 125/3</h2><p>German precision engineering delivers a virtually dust-free sanding experience. The multi-jetstream system and brushless motor set the industry standard for finish quality.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P9LFQ5P?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: BLACK+DECKER BDERO100</h2><p>Perfect for homeowners tackling furniture refinishing and DIY projects. Compact design and 12,000 OPM speed handle most home applications.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00MLSS1SW?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Cordless: Makita XOB01Z</h2><p>This 18V LXT brushless sander delivers 4-12,000 OPM with 3-stage variable speed. The 3-stage electronic speed control adapts to any material.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01LYCHOB8?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Value: Bosch ROS20VSC</h2><p>Bosch combines quality with value in this 5" palm sander. The dual microfilter dust canister and hook-and-loop pad make for easy cleanup and disc changes.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00BD5HD14?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'jigsaws' => '<p class="lead">Jigsaws excel at curved cuts, intricate patterns, and cutouts. Here are the best we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: Bosch JS470E</h2><p>The <strong>Bosch JS470E</strong> top-handle jigsaw delivers powerful 7.0-amp performance with smooth, precise cuts. The tool-less blade change and 4-orbital action settings handle any material.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00DQWQQ0S?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Cordless: DeWalt DCS334B</h2><p>DeWalt\'s 20V MAX XR brushless jigsaw matches corded power without the cord. The anti-slip grip and variable speed trigger give precise control on curved cuts.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07YD58M6K?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: BLACK+DECKER BDEJS600C</h2><p>This 5-amp jigsaw handles most DIY projects with curve control technology. The wire guard keeps the cut line visible while preventing debris in your face.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00OJ72LHK?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Milwaukee 2737-20</h2><p>Milwaukee\'s M18 FUEL jigsaw features a barrel grip design preferred by finish carpenters. The POWERSTATE brushless motor delivers consistent power through the entire cut.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B079CKD7SD?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Barrel Grip: Makita XVJ02Z</h2><p>This 18V LXT brushless jigsaw features a barrel grip for maximum control. The counterbalance mechanism dramatically reduces vibration for all-day comfort.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07PX2DHLS?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'table-saws' => '<p class="lead">A table saw is the heart of any serious woodworking shop. Here are the best table saws we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DWE7491RS</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DWE7491RS</strong> jobsite table saw combines a 32.5" rip capacity with a rolling stand. The rack and pinion fence system ensures accurate, repeatable cuts every time.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00F2CGXGG?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Portable: DeWalt DCS7485B</h2><p>This 60V MAX FlexVolt table saw delivers cordless convenience with 8.25" cut capacity. Perfect for trim carpenters and remodelers working on-site without power access.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08HK7RZ5J?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: SKIL TS6307-00</h2><p>SKIL\'s 15-amp table saw offers surprising quality at an entry-level price. The integrated folding stand and 25.5" rip capacity suit most home workshops.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07R6VFHVY?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: SawStop JSS-120A60</h2><p>SawStop\'s patented flesh-detection brake technology stops the blade on contact. Worth every penny for the safety alone, plus it cuts beautifully with minimal vibration.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C2HB1JQ?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Contractor: Ridgid R4520</h2><p>Ridgid\'s 13-amp contractor saw delivers 30" rip capacity and lifetime service agreement. The gravity-rise wheeled stand makes transport and storage simple.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07LC2CRPB?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
        'miter-saws' => '<p class="lead">Miter saws make quick, accurate crosscuts and angles. Here are the best we tested in 2025.</p><h2>Top Pick: DeWalt DWS779</h2><p>The <strong>DeWalt DWS779</strong> 12" double-bevel sliding compound miter saw cuts up to 2x16 lumber at 90 degrees. The powerful 15-amp motor and tall sliding fence handle crown molding vertically.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01FX0TQT8?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Cordless: Milwaukee 2739-21HD</h2><p>Milwaukee\'s M18 FUEL 12" dual-bevel sliding miter saw delivers corded performance without the cord. Cuts 500+ baseboard pieces per charge.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07JQ8JVDW?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Budget: Metabo HPT C10FCGS</h2><p>This 10" single-bevel compound miter saw offers great value for homeowners. The 15-amp motor and 52-degree miter range handle most trim projects.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07S2RJQJM?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Premium: Festool Kapex KS 120 REB</h2><p>The Kapex is the gold standard for finish carpenters. Dual lasers, integrated dust collection, and German precision make it worth the investment for professionals.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B003ZXCFXA?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div><h2>Best Compact: Makita XSL06Z</h2><p>This 18V X2 (36V) brushless 10" miter saw fits in a truck bed and still handles 4x6 posts. The direct-drive gearbox eliminates maintenance and increases torque.</p><div class="wp-block-buttons"><div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07MWXGMRX?tag='.$newtag.'" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div>',
    ];
